\id GAL - Dobu NT [dob] -Papua New Guinea 1985 (web version -2013)
\h GALETIA
\toc1 Me Galetia ꞌIdi Leta Paulo ꞌIꞌetoladina
\toc2 Galetia
\toc3 Ga
\mt1 ME GALETIA ꞌIDI LETA
\mt1 PAULO ꞌIꞌETOLADINA
\ip Lowa sena Galetia ꞌena Paulo ꞌiloguguya Yesu manuna, nate ꞌina mwawasa kelose ꞌenaya ta ꞌina toololimana manudi, ꞌenega me Galetia yaudi siemisena, ga muliyega Paulo ꞌipilisinedi, ta ꞌiloguguya sakowasi ꞌaina sena wate ꞌediya.
\ip Muliyega ꞌaina me Yudia sitauya Galetia ga sieꞌita, sigwae, “ꞌIlobwenena be walodaba, be waeYudia be ꞌima loinao wamuliyedi, be wate ꞌeguma waemisa Keliso ꞌenaya, Yaubada ꞌida gwausowala manumi; ta ꞌeguma nigeya waeYudia, nigeya ꞌida gwausowala manumi.”
\ip ꞌEnega Paulo ale ꞌinonona ga nuwana ꞌimwau me Yudia ꞌidi kabo manuna, ga me Galetia ꞌidi leta gete ꞌiꞌetoladina ta ꞌediya ꞌietunena be ꞌaene sisawa, be sida mwalatoni emisa namo Yesu Keliso ꞌenaya sawesawenaya be ꞌenega Yaubada ꞌida gwausowala ꞌediya, ta nigeya me Yudia ꞌidi loinao ꞌadi muliya manuna.
\ip Wate ꞌeguma Yesu taemise, Yaluyaluwa Tabuna uwanao boboꞌadi ꞌatedega sida apwesa; ta ꞌeguma nigeya, bwalada uwanao toꞌumalidi sida apwesa.
\c 1
\s1 Lokagutoki
\p 
\v 1 \x * \xo 1:1 \xt Ga 1:11-12\x*ꞌAboꞌagu Yesu Keliso ꞌina tosimana ꞌebweu, ta ꞌigu etosimana nigeya tomota ꞌidi esinuwega, ta Yesu ꞌina esinuwega, be Tamada Yaubada wate. Tauna Yesu mwawasega ꞌigietoolo limena.
\v 2 Ta yaudi tasidao nidi maꞌegwao bada ꞌamiyami ꞌimi leta ꞌaetunenawa ꞌomi totapwalolo, boda ꞌebweuna ꞌebweuna sena Galetia solanaya, ꞌemiya.
\p 
\v 3 Tamada Yaubada be ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌidi obobomega wada miya boboꞌana.
\v 4 \x * \xo 1:4 \xt Ga 2:19-20; Ta 2:14\x*Manuna Tamada Yaubada ꞌina nuwanuwa gete nadigega, ga Yesu tauna ꞌitagwalena ga ꞌimwawasa ꞌida loegesiyao manudi, be ꞌenega tuta gete toꞌumalina ꞌina waiwaiyega ꞌiꞌetoseyeda,
\v 5 Gete manuna Yaubada ꞌena tada tupu atae. Eimeni.
\s1 Tetela boboꞌana ꞌebweuna namo
\p 
\v 6 ꞌEbe nuwaowana gete ꞌeguya, manuna lowa Yaubada ꞌiesinuwemi be ꞌaene oboboma Keliso ꞌenega waloba, ꞌenega tetelina waemisena, ta walomanini gete tuga ga waguitoyasena, ta mali tetela waemisena.
\v 7 \x * \xo 1:7 \xt Gu 15:1, 24\x*Onaꞌaiꞌaila, Tetela Boboꞌana ꞌebweuna namo, ta nigeya ꞌebweu wate tetela ꞌimiyami, ta esi ꞌaina tomota niꞌatu sigiekwanimi, manuna nuwanuwadi be Keliso tetelina sisaꞌu gelase be ꞌenega sikaboemi.
\v 8 \x * \xo 1:8 \xt 1 Ko 16:22\x*Keliso tetelina wagimi nonona nate ꞌaiꞌailina, ꞌenega geyaꞌabo ꞌebweu yaita saꞌi mali tetela ꞌida ꞌebwaꞌebwaꞌemi. ꞌAboꞌama wate be aniloseyao galewega geyaꞌabo mali tetela ꞌaꞌebwaꞌebwaꞌemi. Ta ꞌeguma yaita tetela boboꞌana ꞌisaꞌu gelasena be ꞌigiedumedumena, mwau ꞌida loba Yaubada ꞌenega.
\v 9 Niꞌatu lowa ꞌasimana ꞌemiya, be gete wate yasimana limana ꞌaene ꞌeguma yaita mali tetela ꞌiꞌebwaꞌemi, ꞌelouya ꞌida loba Yaubada ꞌenega.
\p 
\v 10 \x * \xo 1:10 \xt 1 Te 2:4\x*Mwaꞌadega, tomota nidi ꞌadi tuputupu manuna yanuwanuwa, nai Yaubada ꞌana tuputupu? Manuna ꞌeguma tomota ꞌidi nuwanuwa yaguiguinuwa, nigeya sawesaweguya be Keliso manuna yaetoguinuwa.
\s1 Paulo ꞌina nuwaꞌebuni
\p 
\v 11 \x * \xo 1:11 \xt Md 16:17\x*Gosegwao, wada nuwaꞌiꞌisi ꞌaene tetela boboꞌana yasimanenawa, nigeya tomota ꞌediyega,
\v 12 manuna nigeya tomota ꞌidi simanao nai ꞌidi eꞌitao ꞌediyega, ta esi Yesu Keliso ꞌina eꞌita ꞌeguya ꞌenega.
\v 13 \x * \xo 1:13 \xt Gu 8:3\x*Ta ꞌigu bubuna lowa, tuta nina me Yudia ꞌidi boda solanaya yamiyami, wanonona, ꞌaene Yaubada ꞌina toekalesiyao yagieꞌelouya wawasaedi ta nuwanuwagu be yamutudi.
\v 14 \x * \xo 1:14 \xt Gu 22:3\x*ꞌEnega ꞌagu ꞌepatao Yudia solanaya yaewaiwai sinedi, manuna tubudao ꞌidi bubuna manuna yaetapewa sinabwana ta ꞌagu ꞌepatao ꞌidi etapewa tupwana namo.
\p 
\v 15 \x * \xo 1:15 \xt Ais 49:1; Gu 9:3-6\x*Tuta nina nigeya yatubutubuwa, ta lowaenei Yaubada ꞌina obobomega ꞌigimi esinuwegu,
\v 16 ta tauna ꞌina nuwenuwega Natuna ꞌeguya ꞌieꞌitaena, be yada etosimana manuna, sena apwesa ꞌediya. ꞌEnega nigeya yatautauya tomota ꞌediya sabi enaida tetela gete manuna.
\v 17 Nigeya yatautauya Yelusalema Keliso ꞌana gimi tosimanao ꞌediya, ta esi yatauya Alebia, ga nada yamiyami ꞌana laba yaila limana Damasiko ꞌenaya.
\p 
\v 18 ꞌEnega yakwala ꞌetoi mulinaya yalaga Yelusalema ga Pita yayausina, ta nada maꞌiyagu ꞌasiyata pipitini ꞌamiyami.
\v 19 \x * \xo 1:19 \xt Md 13:55\x*Ta Keliso ꞌana tosimanao yaudi nigeya yada ꞌitedi. Nate namo Yemesa, tauna ꞌida ꞌInapwana nina tasina.
\v 20 ꞌIgu ona gete Tamada matanaya yaꞌetoladinawa nigeya ꞌebweu wate kabo.
\p 
\v 21 ꞌEnega Yelusalema yapilisinena ga yatauya Silia be Silisia ꞌidi senao ꞌediya.
\v 22 Ta tuta nidi ꞌediya Keliso ꞌina toekalesiyao Yudia senanao ꞌediya maninigu nigeya sida mwalatonina.
\v 23 Nate namo teteligu sinonona ꞌaene “Tauna lowa ꞌigiegie ꞌelouyeda, ta niꞌatu ꞌinuwaꞌebuni, ga tetela nina lowa ꞌiꞌetoꞌetobodena tuta gete ꞌiloguloguguyae.”
\v 24 ꞌEnega toekalesiyao nidi Yaubada situpuna ꞌigu nuwaꞌebuni manuna.
\c 2
\s1 Keliso ꞌana tosimanao sitagwala Paulo ꞌina loguguya ꞌenaya
\p 
\v 1 ꞌEnega yakwala potini sigumwala, Banaba maꞌiyagu ꞌatuꞌe limana Yelusalema, ga wate Taito yaꞌauꞌewena, ga maꞌemai ꞌatuꞌe.
\p 
\v 2 Ta ꞌigu tauya ꞌalena manuna Yaubada ꞌieꞌitegu ꞌaene ꞌilobwenegu be yada tuꞌe Yelusalema, ꞌenega yatauya toekalesiyao ꞌidi toanuganao ꞌediya, ga taumamo ꞌaꞌawaꞌawagwae, ga tetela nina yaloguloguguya taudi nigeya me Yudia ꞌediya yasimana apwesa toanuganao nidi ꞌediya, manuna geya nuwagu be yaloguguya besobeso, ꞌenega toanuganao nidi sitagwala ꞌigu loguguya nina ꞌenaya.
\p 
\v 3 Ta Taito ꞌiꞌoayabuma ga ꞌatuꞌe Yelusalema, tauna goma Gilisi ꞌebweu, ta esi toanuganao nidi nigeya Taito nina siloiloine be ꞌaene bwalana silodalodaba ꞌana weꞌiweꞌiyaya nadigega taudi.
\v 4 \x * \xo 2:4 \xt Gu 15:1, 24\x*Ta ꞌaidi wate gosedao kabokabodi niꞌatu ꞌemaya siluguma, nuwanuwadi be ꞌida miya boboꞌana Yesu Keliso ꞌiꞌebwaꞌeda sida ꞌita, ta taudi nigeya toemisa ꞌaiꞌaila, manuna nuwanuwadi be loina mwauna siꞌebwaꞌema.
\v 5 ꞌEnega ꞌidi loina maiboꞌana ꞌaguitoyasena, ta nigeya ꞌebweu toꞌase ꞌena ꞌatagwatagwala. Geyaꞌabo ꞌida tetela ꞌaiꞌaila manumi sisaꞌusaꞌu gelasa.
\v 6 \x * \xo 2:6 \xt Gu 10:34\x*Ta wate taudi toekalesiyao sieesedi ꞌaene ꞌidi toanuganao, taudi nigeya ꞌebweu wate loeposeyana sisaꞌusaꞌu ꞌigu loguguya ꞌenaya. Ta ꞌaboꞌagu ꞌigu nuwanuwa ꞌaene nigeya yage sinabwana ꞌeguma taudi sieesedi toanuganao nai toꞌase, manuna tomota maiboꞌada leleleya Yaubada matanaya.
\p 
\v 7 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, toanuganao nidi Yaubada ꞌina egueguyai siꞌitalobena ꞌaene ꞌaboꞌagu tetela boboꞌana yaloguloguguyae taudi nigeya me Yudia ꞌediya, ta Pita esiya me Yudia dimo ꞌediya.
\v 8 Manuna Yaubada Pita waiwai ꞌiꞌebwaꞌena ꞌina guinuwa me Yudia manudi, ta ꞌaboꞌagu wate nadigega waiwai ꞌiꞌebwaꞌegu ꞌigu guinuwa taudi nigeya me Yudia manudi.
\p 
\v 9 \x * \xo 2:9 \xt Gu 11:29-30\x*ꞌEnega toanuganao nidi, Yemesa be Pita be Yoni, Yaubada ꞌina oboboma ꞌeguya siꞌitalobena, ꞌenega sitagwala Banaba be ꞌaboꞌagu ꞌemaya, ga maꞌemao ꞌaenimalotuna. Onaꞌaiꞌaila, toekalesiyao nidi sitetoi getedi sieesedi ꞌadi toanuganao, ta sitetoi nidi sitagwala ꞌemaya be ꞌaene ꞌaboꞌagu be Banaba ꞌatatauya taudi nigeya me Yudia ꞌediya, ta taudi sitatauya me Yudia namo ꞌediya.
\v 10 Ta ꞌebweu yage manuna sigie nuwaꞌiꞌisima, ꞌaene gomabesoyao ꞌada lemedi, be toꞌase ꞌenega sikukupa ꞌada ꞌebwaꞌedi. Yage gete ꞌiboboꞌana wawasae be tuta yauyauna yaetaetapewa waiwai manuna.
\s1 Paulo Pita ꞌiona debedebena
\p 
\v 11 ꞌEnega muliyega tuta nina Pita ꞌimai Anitioki ꞌenaya, ga nada ꞌina bubuna nigeya palupaludi, ꞌenega yaona debedebena ꞌina bubuna toꞌumalina manuna.
\v 12 \x * \xo 2:12 \xt Gu 11:2-3\x*Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌina gimimai ꞌenaya ꞌina bubuna boboꞌana, ꞌenega toekalesiyao taudi nigeya me Yudia ꞌiegosigosiyanedi ta maꞌedi siꞌeꞌai, ta muliyega ꞌaidi Yemesa ꞌina bodao simai, ga Pita me Yudia nidi ꞌimatautedi, ta ꞌenega ꞌeꞌai taudi nigeya me Yudia maꞌenao ꞌiguitoyasa, ta ꞌiebesinedi. Nate Pita ꞌina loegesi.
\v 13 ꞌEnega me Yudia yaudi wate sikabo, ga Banaba wate ꞌidi kabo nina ꞌimuliyena, nate ꞌaene toekalesiyao taudi nigeya me Yudia maꞌediyao geyaꞌabo sida ꞌeꞌai.
\p 
\v 14 ꞌEnega ꞌaboꞌagu yamwalatonina ꞌaene Keliso tetelina palupaluna geyaꞌabo simulimuliya ꞌaiꞌaili, ta maiboꞌadi matadiya Pita yaenaidena, yagwae, “Gosiyagu, ꞌoyo goma Yudiayo, ta ꞌaina tuta me Yudia ꞌida bubuna wapilipilisine be mali sena bubunidi ꞌuetoetotowanedi, ꞌenega mwaꞌadega be taudi mali sena nina tomotenidi ꞌugie sanaila ꞌesedima be Yudia bubunina simuliye?”
\s1 Yaubada ꞌiꞌawa boboꞌaneda ꞌida emisa namo ꞌenega
\p 
\v 15 Taudi nigeya me Yudia sena maiboꞌadi ꞌediya totoꞌumalidi tuga, ta ꞌaboꞌada esi me Yudia,
\v 16 \x * \xo 2:16 \xt Lo 3:20-28, 11:6\x*ꞌenega tamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene Yaubada tomota ꞌiꞌawaꞌawa palupaluyeda nigeya Mosese ꞌina loina ꞌana ematamatana ꞌenega, ta esi ꞌida emisa Yesu Keliso ꞌenaya ꞌenega. Manuna ꞌaboꞌada ꞌida emisa Yesu Keliso ꞌena tasaꞌuna be Yaubada ꞌiꞌawa palupaluyeda. Ta esi ꞌida emisa nigeya Mosese ꞌina loina ꞌana ematamatana ꞌena tasaꞌusaꞌu, manuna Yaubada nigeya tomota ꞌiꞌawaꞌawa palupaluyeda Mosese ꞌina loina ꞌana ematamatana manuna.
\p 
\v 17 Maiboꞌama me Yudia nuwanuwama be Keliso ꞌina guinuwa ꞌenega Yaubada ꞌiꞌawa palupaluyema. Ta ꞌabo ꞌaina tuta ꞌaneneta nai ꞌaloegesi, mwaꞌadega gete, sana Keliso ꞌigiegie loegesiyema? Nigeya.
\p 
\v 18 ꞌAboꞌagu ꞌeguma yaila limana be ꞌigu emisa Mosese ꞌina loinao ꞌediya yasaꞌu, nate yatoꞌumalina.
\v 19 \x * \xo 2:19 \xt Lo 6:6, 7:6; Yo 13:1; Ga 1:4\x*Manuna Mosese ꞌina loina nina niꞌatu ꞌiloemwawasigu, ga muliyega ꞌina waiwai ꞌeguyega ꞌigumwala, be ꞌaene yawasi ꞌaiꞌaila yaloba Yaubada manuna.
\p 
\v 20 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, Keliso maꞌiyagu niꞌatu sigiekeloseyema, ꞌenega mwawamwawasigu ta nigeya taugu yawasiguyega ta esi Keliso yawasina ꞌeguya ꞌimiyami. Gete tuga mayawasigu yamiyami, ta yawasiguna ꞌalena nate ꞌigu emisa Yaubada Natuna ꞌenaya. Manuna Yesu nina ꞌina obobomega tauna ꞌitagwalena ga manugu ꞌimwawasa.
\p 
\v 21 ꞌEnega geyaꞌabo Yaubada ꞌina oboboma nina yaeꞌidiꞌidiye. Geyaꞌabo tanuwanuwa ꞌaene Mosese ꞌina loinao ꞌadi ematamatana ꞌenega Yaubada ꞌida ꞌawa boboꞌaneda. Nate be Keliso ꞌina mwawasa nina ꞌieyage besobeso.
\c 3
\s1 Emisa Keliso ꞌenaya
\p 
\v 1 ꞌOmi me Galetia uwauwami! Yaita sana ꞌilonabwasuwemi ga ꞌigiekwanimi? Lowa ꞌaeꞌitemi ga nuwami ꞌisabwalena ꞌaiꞌaila Yesu Keliso manuna, ꞌaene keloseya ꞌimwawasa ta saꞌi wanuwa pupulena! ꞌEnega wanuwena ꞌaene Mosese ꞌina loina ꞌana ematamatanega ꞌetoseyana walobai?
\v 2 ꞌEnega ꞌebweu enaida yaenaidemi, “To ꞌeda ꞌenega Yaluyaluwa Tabuna waꞌewena? Mosese ꞌina loina ꞌana guinuwao ꞌenega? nai Keliso tetelina wanonona ga waemisena ꞌenega?
\v 3 Uwauwami! ꞌImi tapwalolo ꞌina eꞌale wamwalatonina ꞌaene Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌenega, ꞌenega geyaꞌabo watootoo be ꞌimi tapwalolo wada losaloni taumi ꞌimi guinuwa namo ꞌenega!
\v 4 Sana mwaꞌadega ga ꞌenega yage maiboꞌana waꞌitaloba yogenedi, ga ꞌenega Keliso ꞌana emisa ꞌena wasoꞌi yoge?
\p 
\v 5 ꞌEbweu wate enaida: Yaubada tauna Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌiꞌebwaꞌebwaya ꞌemiya, ta ꞌina waiwaiyega ꞌimi guinuwa waiwaidi waguiguinuwedi. Mwaꞌadega ꞌina ꞌebwaya nidi ꞌemiya Mosese ꞌina loinao ꞌadi guinuwa ꞌenega, nai Keliso tetelina ꞌana emisa ꞌenega?
\p 
\v 6 \x * \xo 3:6 \xt Nug 15:6\x*Wanuwaꞌiꞌisi Ebelaamo ꞌaene tauna Yaubada ꞌiemisena, ꞌenega Yaubada ꞌiꞌawa palupaluyena,
\v 7 be wada mwalatoni ꞌaene Yaubada ꞌana toemisao taudi Ebelaamo natunao.
\p 
\v 8 \x * \xo 3:8 \xt Nug 12:3; Gu 3:25\x*Lowaenei Yaubada Ebelaamo ꞌieonena, ꞌigwae,
\p “ꞌOyo ꞌemuyega maꞌetamo taudi nigeya me Yudia ꞌidi ꞌebe gwausowala sida loba.”
\p Ta Yaubada ꞌina ona gete Buki Tabu solanaya ꞌigimi simanena, sena yaudi ꞌadi giepalupalu Yaubada ꞌana emisa ꞌenega manuna.
\p 
\v 9 \x * \xo 3:9 \xt Lo 4:16\x*ꞌEnega tamwalatonina toemisao maiboꞌadi ꞌaene toemisa nina Ebelaamo maꞌenao ꞌidi ꞌebe gwausowala siloba.
\p 
\v 10 \x * \xo 3:10 \xt 2 Loi 27:26\x*Ta esi ꞌeguma yaisigedi sinuwena ꞌaene Mosese ꞌina loina ꞌana ematamatana ꞌenega sida boboꞌana, ꞌawatoꞌumali namo sida loba, manuna Buki Tabu ꞌigwae,
\p “Loina maiboꞌadi buki gete solanaya ꞌabo yaita nigeya ꞌimuliya ꞌaiꞌailidi, ꞌawatoꞌumali ꞌida loba.”
\p 
\v 11 \x * \xo 3:11 \xt Ga 2:16\x*Onaꞌaiꞌaila, nigeya sawesawenaya be Yaubada tomota ꞌiꞌawa palupaluyeda ꞌabo Mosese ꞌina loina namo taematamatanena. Manuna ona ꞌigwae,
\p “Topalupaludi ꞌidi emisega yawasi boboꞌana sida loba.”
\p 
\v 12 \x * \xo 3:12 \xt Lo 10:5\x*Ta esi Mosese ꞌina loina ꞌana ꞌeda dumadumana, ta emisa ꞌana ꞌeda dumadumana. Loina ꞌana ꞌeda Buki Tabu ꞌena gete nadigega siꞌetoladina, ꞌigwae,
\p “ꞌEguma yaita loina maiboꞌana ꞌiematamatanedi, yawasi boboꞌana ꞌida loba.”
\p 
\v 13 \x * \xo 3:13 \xt 2 Loi 21:22-23; 2 Ko 5:21\x*Ta nigeya sawesawenaya be loina maiboꞌadi taematamatanedi, ꞌenega Keliso nina ꞌilopaꞌeluda ga ꞌiꞌetoseyeda loina ꞌana mwau ꞌenega. Loina ꞌana mwau gete ꞌeguma nigeya tada ematamatanediya tamwamwawasa, ꞌenega Keliso ꞌaboꞌada manuda ꞌimwawasa nadigega taudi totoꞌumalidi sinabwadi ꞌadi loemwawasa kelose ꞌediya. Buki Tabu lowa ꞌina ona gete manuna ꞌigwae,
\p “ꞌAbo yaisigedi kelose ꞌediya sisaꞌudi be simwamwawasa,
\p tomwawasa nidi ꞌawa toꞌumali siloba Yaubada ꞌenega.”
\p Ga Keliso ꞌaboꞌada manuda mwau nina ꞌilobena.
\p 
\v 14 Be Yesu Keliso ꞌenega taudi nigeya me Yudia gwausowala siloba, nadigega gwausowala nina Yaubada ꞌiona upaupaena Ebelaamo ꞌenaya, ꞌaene maiboꞌada ꞌida emisega toꞌase Yaubada ꞌiona upaupaenaya ꞌiꞌebwaꞌeda, nate Yaluyaluwa Tabuna.
\s1 Ona upaupa manuna
\p 
\v 15 Gosegwao, ꞌebweu lewasaꞌiꞌi ꞌida bubuna ꞌenega yaꞌebwaꞌemi, gete nadigega:
\p ꞌEguma tai ꞌiabe ꞌimwamwawasa, ta ꞌina gwegwe nai ꞌebeloina ꞌiꞌebwaꞌe waana ꞌenaya, ꞌina ona nidi nigeya ꞌebweu yaita sawesawenaya be ꞌida saꞌugelasedi.
\p 
\v 16 \x * \xo 3:16 \xt Lu 1:54-55; Nug 12:7\x*Nadigega wate Yaubada ꞌina ona Ebelaamo ma ina susu ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi. Nigeya ꞌaene Buki Tabu ꞌigwae, “Susuyao ꞌediya,” ta esi ꞌina susu ꞌebweuna namo ꞌena, nate Keliso.
\p 
\v 17 \x * \xo 3:17 \xt Gu 7:6\x*ꞌAna mwalatoi gete Yaubada ꞌina onaupaupa ꞌigimi saꞌuna Ebelaamo ꞌenaya, ꞌenega yakwala powa analedi be teti muliyega Mosese ꞌina loina ꞌiapwesa. Ta nigeya sawesawenaya onaupaupa ꞌikweu, nai ꞌisaꞌugelase loina nina ꞌenega, ta esi ma ina waiwai ꞌetamo ꞌimiyami.
\p 
\v 18 \x * \xo 3:18 \xt Lo 4:14, 11:6\x*Wanuwaꞌiꞌisi ꞌeguma ꞌida ꞌebe gwausowala taloba Mosese ꞌina loinega nate ꞌaene nigeya Yaubada ꞌina onaupaupa ꞌenega. Nigeya. Manuna lowa Yaubada ꞌiona upaupaena Ebelaamo ꞌenaya.
\p 
\v 19 \x * \xo 3:19 \xt Lo 5:20\x*Ta toꞌase manuna loina ꞌiapwesa? Loina nina ꞌigieapwesena ꞌedaya ꞌida loegesiyao manudi be ꞌedaya ꞌimiyami ꞌana laba Ebelaamo ꞌina susu nina Yaubada ꞌiona upaupaenaya ꞌiapwesama.
\p Ta loina nina aniloseyao ꞌediyega Yaubada Mosese ꞌiꞌebwaꞌena, ta Mosese ꞌiꞌebwaꞌena tomota ꞌediya.
\v 20 Ta Yaubada ꞌina onaupaupa ꞌina ꞌebwaya dumadumana, manuna Yaubada tauna ꞌiꞌebwaya palupalu Ebelaamo ꞌenaya.
\s1 ꞌIda emisega Yaubada ꞌiꞌawa natuneda
\p 
\v 21 \x * \xo 3:21 \xt Lo 8:2-4\x*Geyaꞌabo wanuwanuwa ꞌaene Mosese ꞌina loina Yaubada ꞌina onaupaupa ꞌietalauwalena? Manuna nigeya ꞌebweu wate loina sawesawenaya be yawasida ꞌiꞌebwaꞌeda, nai ꞌida bubuna ꞌida giepaepaluyedi. Nigeya.
\v 22 \x * \xo 3:22 \xt Lo 3:9-19\x*Ta esi Buki Tabu maiboꞌada ꞌiꞌawa toꞌumaliyeda, ꞌenega Yesu Keliso ꞌana toemisao dimo Yaubada ꞌina onaupaupa siloba.
\p 
\v 23 Lowa tuta nina emisa nigeya tamwalamwalatoni, ꞌaboꞌada Mosese ꞌina loina ꞌiyonida ga tamiya mwau, ga ꞌana laba Yaubada emisa ꞌigieapwesena ꞌedaya.
\v 24 ꞌAna ꞌita ꞌatuwa loina nina ꞌiꞌitaꞌiꞌisida ga ꞌana laba Keliso ꞌiapwesa, be ꞌida emisa ꞌenaya manuna Yaubada ꞌiꞌawa boboꞌaneda.
\v 25 Gete tuga Keliso niꞌatu ꞌimai, ꞌenega loina ꞌina ꞌitaꞌiꞌita ꞌedaya ꞌigumwala,
\v 26 \x * \xo 3:26 \xt Yo 1:12\x*ta esi ꞌida emisega Yaubada maiboꞌada ꞌiꞌawa natuneda, Yesu Keliso maꞌedai.
\v 27 \x * \xo 3:27 \xt Lo 6:3-4, 13:14\x*Manuna yaisigedi ꞌomi wabapitaiso Yesu Keliso ꞌana esanega niꞌatu Keliso nina maꞌemi wamiyami.
\v 28 \x * \xo 3:28 \xt 1 Ko 12:12-14\x*Manuna maiboꞌada Keliso maꞌeda, ta nigeya ꞌebweu wate weyala soladaya ꞌimiyami. ꞌEnega me Yudia be mali bodao leleleya, ta ꞌinapwanao be ꞌidi topaisewao leleleya, ta wate meꞌolotodi be mewainedi leleleya, manuna maiboꞌada Yesu Keliso ꞌenega taeꞌebweu,
\v 29 be maiboꞌada Ebelaamo ꞌina susuyao, manuna maiboꞌada Keliso ꞌina bodao, ꞌenega Yaubada ꞌina onaupaupa Ebelaamo ꞌenaya taꞌewena.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 ꞌEguma yaita ꞌina tuta gwama ꞌenaya ta tamana ꞌina ꞌebeloina ꞌiꞌebwaꞌe, gwama nina geyaꞌabo ꞌietoetoloina, ta esi ꞌietopaisewa,
\v 2 be ꞌina toeꞌitao ꞌenadi ꞌida ematamatane nugana, be ꞌana laba to tuta tamana ꞌitatagwala be natunana ꞌietoloina.
\p 
\v 3 \x * \xo 4:3 \xt Kol 3:20-23\x*ꞌAboꞌada nadigega, manuna lowa ꞌida gimi ꞌebe emisao manudi taetoguinuwa,
\v 4-5 \x * \xo 4:4-5 \xt Yo 1:14; Lo 8:3-4\x*ta muliyega Yaubada natuna ꞌina tuta boboꞌana ꞌilobena, ga natuna ꞌietunenama, ta sinana ꞌienatunena, ga ꞌietomotai ꞌemaya, nate ꞌaboꞌama Mosese ꞌina loinao siyoniyonima, be ꞌediyega ꞌida ꞌetoseyema, ta ꞌomi wate ꞌida ꞌetoseyemi, be Yaubada maiboꞌada ida ꞌawanatuneda.
\v 6 \x * \xo 4:6 \xt Lo 8:15-16\x*ꞌEnega wate Yaubada Natuna yaluyaluwana ꞌatedaya ꞌisaꞌuna, ga Yaubada nina ꞌiꞌawa tamanena, ꞌigwae, “Aba!\f + \fr 4:6 \fk Aba: \ft Ona gete me Yudia ꞌenadi, ꞌana mwalatoi, Tamagu.\f* Tamagu!”
\v 7 \x * \xo 4:7 \xt Lo 8:17; Ga 3:29\x*Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌomi nigeya ꞌaene ꞌina toguinuwa namo, ta esi natunao, ꞌenega maꞌetamo ꞌina gwegwe ꞌiꞌebwaꞌemi, nadigega ꞌina onaupaupa.
\s1 Me Galetia nidi Paulo nuwanuwana
\p 
\v 8 \x * \xo 4:8 \xt 1 Ko 8:4-6\x*ꞌOmi lowa Yaubada nigeya wamwalamwalatoni, ta ꞌimi ꞌebe emisao baleꞌu gwegwenao ꞌediya, taudi nadigega yaubada kabokabodi.
\v 9 Ta gete tugai Yaubada wamwalamwalatoni, nai tagwae Yaubada ꞌimwalatonimi. ꞌEnega toꞌase manuna Yaubada nina waguitoyasena, ta waila limana be ꞌimi ꞌebe emisao nidi nenetadi nuwanuwami, be manudi wada guinuwa limana.
\v 10 \x * \xo 4:10 \xt Kol 2:16\x*ꞌEnega waguiguinuwa emisa kadekadelina manuna, be ꞌaina ꞌasiyata nai nawalae, nai yakwala, nai mali tuta be mali tuta manudi, ꞌimi guinuwao waguiguinuwedi.
\v 11 Gete manuna yaꞌatesaꞌala, ꞌabona nai ꞌigu paisewa nidi ꞌemiya waeyage besobesoedi.
\p 
\v 12 Tasigwao, niꞌatu ꞌami boda ꞌena yalugu ga ꞌaboꞌagu ꞌatuwa nadigega ꞌomi, ꞌenega ꞌilobwenemi be ꞌomi wabubuna ꞌaboꞌagu nadigega. Nigeya ꞌebweu toꞌumalina ꞌeguya waguiguinuwe.
\v 13 \x * \xo 4:13 \xt 1 Ko 2:3\x*Ta wanuwayaina ꞌaene lowa yagimi waiya ꞌemiya ma igu leꞌoasa, ta tuwa tuga tetela boboꞌana yaloguguyaena ꞌemiya.
\v 14 Ta nigeya waeꞌidiꞌidiyegu oogu ꞌina neneta manuna, ta esi watagwalemi ꞌeguya, ga waꞌauꞌeweguya ꞌatuwa nadigega Yaubada ꞌina anilose ꞌebweu, nai Yesu Keliso.
\p 
\v 15 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, waꞌawa gosiyana ꞌaiꞌailegu, be ꞌabo sawesawenaya matamiyega wada iwayauledi be waꞌebwaꞌegu, matagu toꞌumalidi ꞌadi lopaꞌelu. Ta gete tugai mwaꞌadega ꞌida egosigosiyana nina?
\v 16 \x * \xo 4:16 \xt Yo 8:45\x*ꞌAna ꞌita niꞌatu waetalauwalegu manuna simana ꞌaiꞌaila yaꞌebwaꞌemi.
\p 
\v 17 ꞌImi esaꞌugelasa ꞌalena ꞌimi toeꞌitao auwaudi niꞌatu sietaetapewa manumi, ta esi sikabokaboemi. Taudi nuwanuwadi be ꞌigu loina waguitoyase be ꞌidi loinega nuwami sida ꞌewa.
\p 
\v 18 ꞌIgu loina gete ꞌeguma ꞌaboꞌagu maꞌemiya tamiyami, nai ꞌeguma ꞌemiyega yamiya ꞌedasola, loina ꞌebweuna tuga, nate ꞌilobwenemi be waetapewa guinuwa boboꞌana manuna.
\p 
\v 19 Natugwao, manumi ꞌategu ꞌiuyauya tuta maiboꞌana, ꞌimi sanaila manuna, be ꞌana laba Keliso ꞌemiya ꞌiapwesa limana, be ꞌatemiya ꞌida miyami, be ꞌenega ꞌagu lotoona ꞌida boboꞌana limana.
\p 
\v 20 ꞌEguma saꞌi ꞌomi maꞌegwao tada miyami, be ꞌenega wada nuwaꞌebuni be ꞌagu lotoona ꞌida boboꞌana, ta esi niꞌatu yanuwanuwa sinabwana ꞌimi toꞌumalina manuna.
\s1 Ega be Sela tetelidi
\p 
\v 21 ꞌOmi nuwanuwami be Mosese ꞌina loinao wada muliyedi, ta esi ꞌadi mwalatoi nigeya wamwalamwalatonidi.
\v 22 \x * \xo 4:22 \xt Nug 16:15, 21:2\x*Wada nuwaꞌiꞌisi Ebelaamo tetelina ꞌetoꞌetoladina, natunao meꞌolotodi ꞌeluwa, ꞌebweuna ꞌina ꞌaliꞌei mewainena ꞌenega, ta ꞌeluwena mwaneꞌaiꞌailina ꞌenega.
\v 23 \x * \xo 4:23 \xt Lo 9:7-9\x*ꞌAliꞌei nina ꞌana esana Ega, ta mwanena Sela, ga Ega ꞌina ꞌeuwana bubuna baleꞌu ꞌenega, ta Sela ꞌina ꞌeuwana Yaubada ꞌina onaupaupa ꞌenega, ga natuna ꞌana esana Aisake.
\v 24 \x * \xo 4:24 \xt Lo 8:15\x*Ga iine nidi tetelidi ꞌenega ꞌebeꞌita talobena gete: Ega natunao ꞌienatunedi topaisewa yoniyonidi,
\v 25 ta ꞌidi sena Alebia solanaya, ꞌoya ꞌebweuna, ꞌana esana Sainai, ta Sainai ꞌana mwalatoi ꞌaene taudi me Yelusalema batuwa nadigega, manuna batuwa ꞌatuwa tomota yoniyonidi Mosese ꞌina loinao ꞌediyega.
\p 
\v 26 \x * \xo 4:26 \xt Ib 12:22; Et 21:2, 10\x*Ta ꞌaboꞌada nigeya yoniyonida, ta ꞌida sena Yelusalema galewaya, ꞌatuwa sinada ꞌienatuneda Yaubada ꞌina onaupaupa ꞌenega.
\p 
\v 27 \x * \xo 4:27 \xt Ais 54:1\x*Yage gete manuna Buki Tabu ꞌena siꞌetoladina, ꞌigwae:
\p “Waine ꞌoyo megagalina ꞌuda gwausowala. Lowa nigeya ꞌuda edadama be ꞌuda enatuna, ta esi ꞌuda gwausowala sinabwana natumwao yau wawasae manudi, ta waine nina mamwanena simiyami manatudiyao, ta nigeya yaudi.”
\p 
\v 28 Gosegwao, ꞌaboꞌada Aisake nadigega, manuna Aisake sinana ꞌimegagala, ta muliyega Yaubada ꞌina onaupaupa manuna ga ꞌienatuna.
\p 
\v 29 Ta Isimeeli Aisake ꞌietalauwalena. ꞌEbeꞌita gete, tauna bubuna baleꞌu ꞌenega ꞌitubuwa ꞌietalauwalaya tauna onaupaupa ꞌenega ꞌitubuwa. Lowa taudi siteluwa nidi nadigega, ga batuwa wate nadigega tomota gosediyao sibubunaꞌesedi.
\p 
\v 30 \x * \xo 4:30 \xt Nug 21:10; Yo 8:35\x*Ta Buki Tabu solanaya loina ꞌetoꞌetoladina ꞌigwae,
\p “ꞌAliꞌei nina manatuna ꞌupaꞌi apwesedi. Geyaꞌabo
\p ꞌaliꞌei natuna be natuꞌaiꞌailiyo siloiloina leleleya.
\p Ta esi Aisake namo ꞌebeloina ꞌida ꞌewa.”
\p 
\v 31 ꞌAboꞌada nigeya Isimeeli nadigega, manuna Isimeeli topaisewa yoniyonina natuna, ta ꞌaboꞌada Aisake nadigega ga ꞌida miya boboꞌana.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 \x * \xo 5:1 \xt Yo 8:32, 36; Gu 15:10\x*Miya boboꞌana manuna Keliso ꞌiliꞌamida ꞌada yonao ꞌediyega, ꞌenega wada toolopaꞌala be geyaꞌabo watagwatagwala limanemi Mosese ꞌina loina yoniyonina ꞌenaya.
\s1 Keliso ꞌina loina boboꞌana
\p 
\v 2 ꞌAboꞌagu Paulo yaloguguya ꞌemiya be ꞌabo Mosese ꞌina loinao ꞌediya watagwalemi, nai ꞌabo me Yudia ꞌidi weꞌiweꞌiyaya lodaba\f + \fr 5:2 \fk daba nai lodaba: \ft Nugana 17:10-14 ꞌena Yaubada Ebelaamo ꞌiloinena be ꞌaene tauna be natunao meꞌolotodi be tubunao meꞌolotodi ꞌidi yage bwaladi sida ꞌupwa yauledi, nate weꞌiweꞌiyaya nai ꞌebe ꞌinana sida guinuwe, ta ꞌana mwalatoi taudi Yaubada ꞌina tomotaiyao esiesinuwadi.\f* bwalamiya sida guinuwe, Keliso ꞌina lema ꞌemiya waloseye.
\v 3 Manuna ꞌeguma yaita ꞌemiyega ꞌitagwale be bwalana silodabai, ꞌilobwene be Mosese ꞌina loinao maiboꞌadi wate ꞌida ematamatanedi,
\v 4 be ꞌabo yaita ꞌoyo nuwanuwayo be Mosese ꞌina loinao ꞌadi ematamatana ꞌenega ꞌawaboboꞌana ꞌuda loba, niꞌatu Keliso ꞌina oboboma ꞌemuya ꞌuloseyena, ga tauna ꞌupilisinena.
\p 
\v 5 Manuna ꞌaboꞌada Yaubada taemisena be ꞌaene ꞌiꞌawa palupaluyeda. Gete ꞌida nuwayaina Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌenega, ga manuna tayamwayamwa.
\p 
\v 6 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, Yesu Keliso ꞌenaya me Yudia ꞌadi weꞌiweꞌiyaya, nate bwaladi silodaba, nigeya ꞌigiepaepaluyeda, be wate ꞌabo lodaba taguitoyase geyaꞌabo ꞌada ꞌawapalupalu talobaloba. Nate namo ꞌeguma Yesu taemise be taobobome, tauna ꞌada togiepalu.
\p 
\v 7 ꞌOmi lowa wapili waiwai emisa ꞌina ꞌeda ꞌaiꞌaila ꞌenega, ꞌenega yaita ꞌisaꞌu bodemi?
\v 8 ꞌEtoboda gete nigeya Yaubada ꞌenega, manuna lowa Yaubada ꞌibwauyemi tauna ꞌina ꞌeda ꞌenaya, ta esi ꞌetoboda gete mali tomota ꞌediyega.
\v 9 Getei ꞌatuwa ꞌebweu yage gidalina, ta esi toꞌumalina, ta sawesawenaya be ꞌigie toꞌumali sinabwana.
\p 
\v 10 ꞌAboꞌagu ꞌInapwana yaemisena be ꞌigienuwa sabwalenimi, be ꞌigu loina namo wada muliye, ta ꞌabo yaita tauna ꞌami togieloniu, ꞌana eꞌisa Yaubada ꞌenega maꞌetamo ꞌiloba.
\p 
\v 11 \x * \xo 5:11 \xt 1 Ko 1:23\x*Gosegwao, geyaꞌabo wanuwena ꞌaboꞌagu yaloguloguguya be ꞌaene tomota sida lodabadi be me Yudia ꞌidi loina sida muliyedi, ta ꞌigu loguguya esi Keliso ꞌina mwawasa kelose ꞌenaya manuna, ta loguguya gete manuna me Yudia sinuwamwau ga sietalauwalegu.
\v 12 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌilobwenena be taudi ꞌami togieloniu nidi taudimo siloꞌewa yauledi be ꞌewaꞌewadi.
\p 
\v 13 \x * \xo 5:13 \xt 1 Pi 2:16\x*Gosegwao, Yaubada niꞌatu ꞌiesinuwemi ga liꞌaliꞌamimi, ta geyaꞌabo wanuwena ꞌaene nigeya ꞌami loinamo be bubuna baleꞌu wamulimuliyedi, ta esi oboboma ꞌina loinega wada tauya be taumimo wada elemalema limanemi.
\p 
\v 14 \x * \xo 5:14 \xt Md 5:43-44, 7:12\x*Manuna loina maiboꞌadi ꞌadi bwagila, loina ꞌebweuna gete, ꞌigwae,
\p “Gosemwao ꞌuda obobomedi nadigega tauyo ꞌamu oboboma.”
\p 
\v 15 ꞌEguma loina gete wapilisine be taumimo ꞌemiya waetalauwala, maꞌetamo ꞌami boda waloesawali.
\s1 Yaluyaluwa uwana dumadumana ta bwala uwana dumadumana
\p 
\v 16 \x * \xo 5:16 \xt Lo 8:3-4\x*ꞌEnega ꞌilobwenemi be Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌianuganemi ta ꞌenega geyaꞌabo yalakwaiyao siloiloinemi.
\v 17 \x * \xo 5:17 \xt Lo 7:15-23\x*Manuna yalakwaiyao Yaluyaluwa Tabuna sietalauwalena, ta saꞌi Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌida yalakwaiyao ꞌietalauwaledi. ꞌEnega soladaya silosalosaiya, ta toꞌase boboꞌana nuwanuwada be taguinuwei nigeya sawesawedaya be taguinuwei.
\v 18 \x * \xo 5:18 \xt Lo 6:14\x*Nate namo ꞌeguma Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌianuganemi, Mosese ꞌina loinao sigugumwala ꞌemiyega.
\p 
\v 19 Ooda ꞌina guinuwao tamwalamwalatonidi, nate loelata, loyawe, gagasa,
\v 20 nabwasuwa, balau, egewagewana, etalauwala, eꞌipiꞌipi, gamwasowala, debaose, weyala, sinala, eꞌidiꞌidi,
\v 21 be wate ꞌebe gwausowala toꞌumalina bwasi waiwai ꞌana numa ꞌenega, ta ꞌaina wate bubuna toꞌumalidi. Bubuna getedi manudi lowa yaemataluwemi, ta batuwa yaemataluwa limami ꞌaene ꞌadi toguinuwao geyaꞌabo Yaubada ꞌina ꞌebeloina ꞌena silugulugu.
\p 
\v 22 \x * \xo 5:22 \xt Md 7:16-20; Ep 5:8-9\x*Ta saꞌi Yaluyaluwa Tabuna uwana boboꞌadi ꞌatedaya getedi, oboboma, gwausowala, miyasiwalowa, toolopaꞌala, lema, bubuna palupaluna, emisa,
\v 23 bubuna nuwana, ꞌalamaꞌiꞌita. Ta nigeya ꞌebweu wate loina ꞌimiyami be yage getedi ꞌida ꞌetobodedi.
\v 24 \x * \xo 5:24 \xt Kol 3:5\x*Ta wate ꞌeguma Yesu Keliso ꞌiloineda, ooda ꞌina bubuna toꞌumalidi be yalakwaiyao ꞌiloemwawasidi ꞌana kelose ꞌenaya.
\v 25 Ta yawasida boboꞌana ꞌiꞌebwaꞌeda Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌenega, ta ꞌilobwenena be Yaluyaluwa nina ꞌianuganeda.
\p 
\v 26 \x * \xo 5:26 \xt Pi 2:3\x*Ta geyaꞌabo tanuwanuwa tuꞌe, nai gosedao taeꞌoataꞌoatadi, nai taeꞌipiꞌipiyedi.
\c 6
\s1 Tada elemalema
\p 
\v 1 \x * \xo 6:1 \xt Md 18:15\x*Gosegwao, ꞌeguma tasidai ꞌebweu ꞌina loegesi ꞌenega ꞌibeꞌu, ꞌomi yaluyaluwami paꞌalidi watoo be tasidai nina wagiepaepaluye, ta esi ma imi bubuna nuwana, be taumimo waꞌitaꞌiꞌisimi, ꞌabona nai ꞌomi wate wabebeꞌu.
\p 
\v 2 \x * \xo 6:2 \xt Lo 15:1-2\x*ꞌAmi ꞌaaꞌaalao ꞌediya wada elemalema magosemiyao, manuna gete ꞌada loina Keliso ꞌenega, ta ꞌilobweneda be taguinuwe.
\p 
\v 3 ꞌEguma yaita gomabeso, ta ꞌinuwena ꞌaene toesaesa, taunamo saꞌi ꞌikaboena.
\v 4 \x * \xo 6:4 \xt 2 Ko 13:5; Lo 14:12\x*ꞌEnega ꞌilobwenemi be ꞌebweuna ꞌebweuna tauna ꞌina guinuwa ꞌida too, be ꞌida mwalatoni mane guinuwa boboꞌana ta mane toꞌumalina. ꞌEnega ꞌeguma boboꞌana, ꞌana tupu tauna ꞌina nuwanuwa ꞌana lotoona ꞌenega, ta geyaꞌabo gosiyana ꞌebweu ꞌina ona ꞌenega.
\v 5 Ta ꞌada ꞌaaꞌaala tauda ꞌebweuna ꞌebweuna tada ꞌaala.
\p 
\v 6 \x * \xo 6:6 \xt 1 Ko 9:11, 14\x*Tapwalolo ꞌana toeꞌitao, ꞌeguma sinasinapu sieꞌitada, ꞌilobweneda be gwegwe taꞌebwaꞌedi, ꞌabo toꞌase ꞌediya ꞌikukupa.
\p 
\v 7 Geyaꞌabo tauyo ꞌukabokaboeyo, manuna nigeya sawesawedaya be Yaubada takaboe. Toꞌase tai ꞌiasona, muliyega ꞌida sesoni.
\v 8 \x * \xo 6:8 \xt Yo 3:6, 6:63; Lo 8:13\x*ꞌEguma bubuna bwala ꞌenega ꞌiasowa, maꞌetamo sesoi toꞌumalina ꞌiloba, ta ꞌeguma Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌenega ꞌiasowa, maꞌetamo yawasi ataya ꞌida sesoni.
\p 
\v 9 \x * \xo 6:9 \xt 2 Te 3:13; 1 Ko 15:58\x*Geyaꞌabo ꞌida guinuwa boboꞌadi ꞌediyega taloꞌameꞌame, manuna ꞌeguma geyaꞌabo taneeneta, maꞌetamo sesoi boboꞌana tada loba.
\v 10 ꞌEnega ꞌilobweneda be tuta maiboꞌana ꞌediya tomota yauyaudi tada lemedi, ta esi Yaubada ꞌana toemisao talemedi sinabwana.
\p 
\v 11 ꞌEtoladi gete matana sinabwana taugu nimaguyega yaꞌetoladina.
\v 12 \x * \xo 6:12 \xt Ga 5:11; Pi 3:18\x*Me Yudia ꞌidi lodaba ꞌana toꞌewao geya nuwadi ꞌigu loguguya nina gete: ꞌada giepaepalu taloba Keliso ꞌina mwawasa namo ꞌenega, ta nigeya lodaba ꞌenega. ꞌEnega siꞌiꞌimimi be ꞌidi lodaba nina waꞌewa, be ꞌadi boda ꞌida sinabwa, ta wate etalauwala Keliso ꞌina mwawasa kelose ꞌenaya manuna ꞌigugumwala.
\v 13 Ta wada nuwaꞌiꞌisi ꞌaene lodaba nina ꞌana toꞌewao ꞌilobwenedi be Mosese ꞌina loinao maiboꞌadi sida muliyedi, ta esi nigeya sida muliyedi. Nate namo nuwanuwadi be walodaba, be gete ꞌidi ꞌebe gagasa ꞌimi lugu ꞌadi boda solanaya manuna.
\v 14 \x * \xo 6:14 \xt Lu 14:27; Ga 2:20-21\x*Ta ꞌaboꞌagu esi geyaꞌabo yaonaona tuꞌe. Nate namo ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌana kelose manuna yada onalaga, manuna Keliso ꞌana kelose ꞌenega bubuna baleꞌu ꞌiloemwawasina ga ꞌina loina ꞌeguya ꞌigumwala, ta wate taudi bubuna baleꞌu ꞌana tomuliyao siguitoyasegu ꞌatuwa tomwawasa ꞌaboꞌagu.
\p 
\v 15 \x * \xo 6:15 \xt 2 Ko 5:17\x*Onaꞌaiꞌaila, lodaba nigeya yage sinabwana, ta wate ꞌeguma nigeya taguiguinuwe nate nigeya yage sinabwana. Yage sinabwana ꞌebweuna namo, ꞌeguma Yaubada yaluyaluwana ꞌigie auwauda.
\v 16 Ta maiboꞌada ꞌeguma loina gete tamulimuliye, ta Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌigie auwauda, ꞌaboꞌada Yaubada ꞌina susu me Isileli ꞌaiꞌaila, be ꞌina ꞌatenuwa ꞌoleꞌoleyega tada miya siwalowa.
\p 
\v 17 \x * \xo 6:17 \xt 2 Ko 4:10\x*Gete tuga be tuta ꞌimeemai ꞌediya geyaꞌabo ꞌebweu yaita ꞌigiegie ꞌoataꞌoatagu, manuna bwalaguya Yesu ꞌina weꞌiweꞌiyaya simiyami, nate kweya nidi yalobedi ꞌina guinuwa ꞌenaya.
\p 
\v 18 Tasigwao, ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌina oboboma yaluyaluwami ꞌediya. Eimeni.
\cls ꞌAboꞌagu Paulo. 
